text: Park Hye-suk (; born 15 July 1964) is a South Korean rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
